@port = 7125

### 1. Test the Login Endpoint
POST https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/login
// Expected: 200 OK & Set-Cookie Header
###

### 2. Login as Organization Manager
POST https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/login/manager
// Expected: 200 OK & Set-Cookie Header

###

### 3. Test Org Endpoint (As Manager)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/roster
// Expected: 200 OK

###

### 4. Test FA Endpoint (As Manager)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/escrow
// Expected: 403 Forbidden (Because Manager has an OrgId)

###

### 5. Logout
POST https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/logout

###

### 6. Login as Free Agent Staff
POST https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/login/freeagent
// Expected: 200 OK & Set-Cookie Header

###

### 7. Test FA Endpoint (As Free Agent)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/escrow
// Expected: 200 OK

###

### 8. Test Org Endpoint (As Free Agent)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/roster
// Expected: 403 Forbidden (Because FA is missing the OrgId claim AND RosterManage permission)

### 9. Test i18n Error Response (English Fallback)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/error
Accept-Language: en-US
// Expected: 400 Bad Request with "Validation Failed" in English

###

### 10. Test i18n Error Response (Portuguese - Brazil)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/error
Accept-Language: pt-BR
// Expected: 400 Bad Request with "Validation Failed" translated to Portuguese

###

### 11. Test i18n Error Response (Spanish)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/error
Accept-Language: es
// Expected: 400 Bad Request with "Validation Failed" translated to Spanish

### 12. Test i18n Error Response (French)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/error
Accept-Language: fr
// Expected: 400 Bad Request with "Validation Failed" translated to French

### 13. Diagnose Current Culture (Spanish)
GET https://localhost:{{port}}/api/auth/test/culture
Accept-Language: es
// Expected: "es"